{
  "texts": [
    "A potential future work is to evaluate LORDD on other causal language modeling tasks, including seq2seq tasks, and other dialects.",
    "Similarly, an extension to LORDD would eliminate the requirement of naturally occurring conversations in multiple dialects.",
    "While previous approaches have proposed dialect adapters as task-agnostic, our study does not make the same claim.",
    "We use target word prediction as the task of predicting the last word of a conversation which was the word that the described was attempting to convey to the guesser.",
    "This task is a simplistic version of causal language modeling."
  ]
}